message:
The error rate when sending push notifications has increased.

{{#is_alert}}To investigate, check the [push notification delivery dashboard](https://app.datadoghq.com/dashboard/ji5-8b7-bp4/mobile-push-notification-delivery) and [search Bugsnag](https://app.bugsnag.com/handshake/handshake/errors?filters[event.since][0]=all&filters[search][0][type]=eq&filters[search][0][value]=SendPushNotification&filters[error.status][0][type]=eq&filters[error.status][0][value]=open&sort=events) for errors in the `SendPushNotification` worker.

Be aware that push notification sends are bursty, and the count of failed sends could fluctuate significantly depending on the amount of push notifications being sent at a given time.{{/is_alert}} 

{{#is_recovery}}
Error rate from sending push notifications has decreased.
{{/is_recovery}}
 @slack-incidents-students,@slack-errors-core
